{{Dialogue Start}}
;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502150001: Config/Level/Mission/5021500/Act/Act502150001.json-->
::'''Su Meile:''' Grab a bottle of SoulGlad, and make your dreams a blast! That {{MC|f=lady|m=gentleman}} over there, would you like a bottle of authentic SoulGlad imported directly from Penacony? Multiply your happiness with some SoulGlad as you watch the competition!
::'''Su Meile:''' During the Drink Up event period, participate in the Uncap and Win event when you purchase SoulGlad. Many exciting rewards are up for grabs!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is your SoulGlad authentic?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150104-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' Of course it's authentic! The reason SoulGlad™ set up an official flagship store on Skysplitter is to ensure that the audience gets to enjoy the most authentic SoulGlad.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you sure the Uncap and Win event is not a scam?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150106-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' Rest assured, {{MC|f=miss|m=mister}}. The prize draw is supervised by the Realm-Keeping Commission and all the prize probabilities have been clearly stated in public.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I gotta know what kinds of prizes you can offer.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150108-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' There are so many! One More Bottle, Miss Robin's concert tickets, Penacony luxury travel packages, and even a year's free supply of SoulGlad!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502150109-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150109-->
::'''Su Meile:''' Here, besides Classic SoulGlad, we also have the Sweet Dreams Soda flavor made exclusively for the Xianzhou folk's tastes... However, I still recommend the classic flavor. Sweet Dreams Soda... cannot provide the ultimate experience of happiness.
::'''Su Meile:''' So, {{MC|f=miss|m=mister}}, how about a bottle of SoulGlad? Promoting products is hard work, you know!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm actually cutting down on sugar these days.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150112-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' Oh... Maybe we should consider releasing a zero sugar version of SoulGlad. Sales... Uh, health matters, after all!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll take one right now!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150114-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' Great! I know I'm starting to sound like a broken record, but beverages as good as SoulGlad? They don't even need promoters &mdash; the taste is enough to speak for itself!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I prefer Immortal's Delight.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150116-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' Huh? No offense, but Immortal's Delight is the reason why Xianzhou folks can't tell yummy from yucky anymore. That beverage is the scourge of the industry, if you ask me.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502150117-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150117-->
::'''Su Meile:''' Well, if you ever feel like a bottle of SoulGlad, just let me know, {{MC|f=miss|m=mister}}!
;(Subsequent interactions)
