::{{DIcon|Talk}} Is SoulGlad selling well in Xianzhou?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150203-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' Not exactly. It's not that easy to penetrate the beverage market here.
:::'''Su Meile:''' For one thing, the locals are highly particular about how their beverages taste. More often than not, beverages from other worlds have to be adapted to cater to the dietary preferences of the Xianzhou people. Sweet Dreams Soda has compromised too much on the flavor &mdash; I feel that you can't really call it "SoulGlad" anymore.
:::'''Su Meile:''' For another, the local beverage brands are all established with long histories, and they're even inexpensive to boot. People aren't willing to splurge much on beverages that they consume on a regular basis.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Slash the prices. Go for low profit but high sales.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150207-->
::::'''Su Meile:''' A price war? Are you sure that would work?
::::'''Su Meile:''' It's true that our prices don't work to our benefit. High-concentration syrup, memoria, cross-galactic freight costs, and even Sky-Faring Commission's import duties... Our production costs are much higher than those of local Xianzhou beverages.
::::'''Su Meile:''' However, SoulGlad™ is planning to heavily invest in the Xianzhou local market. If we set up a factory here, the scales of commerce will definitely start to tip in our favor.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502150214-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150214-->
::::'''Su Meile:''' But for now... Things aren't looking too good on the sales front.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Try changing your marketing strategy?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150211-->
::::'''Su Meile:''' My thoughts exactly. I'm planning to invite a Xianzhou local celeb as our brand ambassador. What kind of celebrity do you think will make a good fit?
::::'''Su Meile:''' A popular influencer like Guinaifen will get plenty of attention from youths, I reckon.
::::'''Su Meile:''' But visitors to the Skysplitter are likely to find Master Yanqing more interesting. We even have the campaign slogan ready: "Chill out with the Frosty Blade. Chill out with a SoulGlad™."
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502150214-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150214-->
::::'''Su Meile:''' But for now... Things aren't looking too good on the sales front.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You don't seem to be promoting Sweet Dreams Soda at all.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150216-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' Mm... I'll put it this way: Sweet Dreams Soda isn't SoulGlad in my book.
:::'''Su Meile:''' Not only does its recipe call for reduced syrup levels, but it even includes local Xianzhou herbs as ingredients. Call the mishmash of flavors what you want, but it's not SoulGlad.
:::'''Su Meile:''' SoulGlad owes its universe-spanning popularity to its one-of-a-kind flavor. By messing up its flavor profile with random additions, it's no different from forsaking what makes SoulGlad sell in the first place. The notion absolutely boggles my mind.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Why are you selling SoulGlad in the Xianzhou?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150220-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' Boss' orders.
:::'''Su Meile:''' I know, I know... It's a disappointing answer. I could spin a grand story about how much I love SoulGlad's culture and how I dream of it becoming a beverage that everybody in the cosmos knows and loves, but I don't want to lie.
:::'''Su Meile:''' According to my boss, I'm the top salesperson in Penacony, and thus the one "most suitable" for trailblazing a path to a new market. "To whom much is given, much is required," or something like that... A ton of empty promises later, the next thing I know, I'd been thrown onto an airship bound for Xianzhou.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have any more questions.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502150224-->
:::'''Su Meile:''' Well, if you ever feel like a bottle of SoulGlad, you know where to find me.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have anything to talk about today.
::'''Su Meile:''' Well, if you ever feel like a bottle of SoulGlad, you know where to find me.
